column5: Anyone have any suggestions for a spot in Ear Falls with a good burger and a cold beer. Will be there Friday. Thanks. Matt
[font color=green size=3][b] Stop at the Sunset Cafe just south of Perault Falls, excellent food and cold beer too.
the little restaurant in the trillium hotel is pretty good also. - phish
Trailerguy is right-The Sunset is a good restaurant. They open early, close late and are fully licensed. Say Hi to Gary for me if you stop there.
